ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this course to fellow students. It helps me develop research ideas to a full paper.

Takes students through the process of coming up with a research idea and writing a publishable article. I would recommend thisto another student because this is a skill that needs to be acquired, and this class helps in this regard.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It was good experience to have this course as a way to develop research ideas to a fullpaper.
